    • insertOne

      public boolean insertOne​(Project object) throws Exception
      Insert one record about project object, and link and file records about it.
      定義:
      insertOne インタフェース内 BaseService<Project>
      パラメータ:
      object - project object to insert (not null. Id for object can be -1)
      戻り値:
      If success to insert the record, then return true
      例外:
      Exception - DB exception about project, and file put exception at files and links data.

    • selectOne

      public Project selectOne​(Project object) throws Exception
      Select one record about project object, and link and file records about it.
      定義:
      selectOne インタフェース内 BaseService<Project>
      パラメータ:
      object - project object which only set id to select data (not null. Id required for object other than -1)
      戻り値:
      Selected project object.(not null) It contains list of links and files about it.(not null, but may be empty list)
      例外:
      Exception - Id is -1 exception, DB exception, data not found exception.

    • selectMany

      public List<Project> selectMany​(Project object) throws Exception
      Select many records about project object, and link and file records about it.
      定義:
      selectMany インタフェース内 BaseService<Project>
      パラメータ:
      object - project object which only user-id to select data (not null. User-id required for object other than "" or null)
      戻り値:
      List of selected project object.(not null, but may be empty list) It contains list of links and files about it.(not null, but may be empty list)
      例外:
      Exception - UserId is none exception, DB exception.

    • updateOne

      public boolean updateOne​(Project object) throws Exception
      Update one record about project object, and link and file records about it.
      定義:
      updateOne インタフェース内 BaseService<Project>
      パラメータ:
      object - project object which set items to update one project data.(not null. Id required for object other than -1) It contains some links and files data.(null is OK)
      戻り値:
      If success to update the record, then return true
      例外:
      Exception - Id is -1 exception, DB exception, and file put exception at files and links data.

    • upsertOne

      public boolean upsertOne​(Project object) throws Exception
      Check for the existence of project object. If it exists then update one project record and some link and file records, else insert them.
      定義:
      upsertOne インタフェース内 BaseService<Project>
      パラメータ:
      object - project object to insert or update (not null. Id for object can be -1)
      戻り値:
      If success to insert or update the record, then return true
      例外:
      Exception - Exception at insert or update data
      Exception - DB exception, and file put exception at files and links data
